import Module from "../../common/module";
 
import MenuController from "./menu-controller";
import Menu from "./menu-directive";
import MenuAction from "./menu-action-directive";
import MenuDivider from "./menu-divider-directive";
import MenuHeader from "./menu-header-directive";
import MenuLink from "./menu-link-directive";
import MenuOption from "./menu-option-directive";
import { MenuService } from "./menu-service";

    module.component("xuiMenu", Menu);
    module.component("xuiMenuAction", MenuAction);
    module.component("xuiMenuDivider", MenuDivider);
    module.component("xuiMenuHeader", MenuHeader);
    module.component("xuiMenuLink", MenuLink);
    module.component("xuiMenuOption", MenuOption);
    module.controller("xuiMenuController", MenuController);
    module.service("xuiMenuService", MenuService);
};
